Data Model 
Query 1 – List of comments by author name, by creating a UDT for comment text
TABLE comments 
Column name	Type
Comment time	date
Comment 	Map(int,Text)
Story		Map(int,Text)
Ranking		int
Author		Text

Primary key (Author)

Query 2 –  Listing the count of stories/ comments from an author

TABLE Stories_Comments
Column name	Type
Unique ID	int
Time		date
Body 		Text
Type		Text
Authors		Text

Primary Key ( Authors, Unique ID)

Query 3 -  Top 50 stories having highest number of descendants
TABLE Stories
Column name	Type
Story ID	int
Time		date
Story		Text
Author		text
No_of_Descendants	int

Primary Key ( Story ID ,No_of_Descendants)

Query 4 - Top ranked stories/comment
TABLE Stories_Comments
Column name	Type
Unique ID	int
Time		date
Body 		Text
Ranking		int
Type		Text

Primary Key ( Unique ID ,Ranking)
